213
00:16:26,040 --> 00:16:26,750
Halo.

214
00:16:26,880 --> 00:16:29,670
Jiashang, ini aku.

215
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:31,240
Aku tahu.

216
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:32,400
♪Di dalam mataku♪

217
00:16:32,400 --> 00:16:33,510
Kau merindukanku?

218
00:16:34,620 --> 00:16:36,750
Katanya cuaca di Shanghai
semakin dingin.

219
00:16:37,160 --> 00:16:39,720
Kau harus pakai baju yang lebih
