225
00:16:49,870 --> 00:16:52,550
(Lalu, memesan semangkuk
pangsit sup bening.)

226
00:16:52,640 --> 00:16:53,760
(Juga segenggam ebi.)

227
00:16:53,760 --> 00:16:54,910
♪Agar tidak berkelana♪

228
00:16:54,910 --> 00:16:56,480
Kau membuatku tergiur.

229
00:16:56,910 --> 00:16:58,720
Sayangnya, aku ada di Beijing.

230
00:16:58,760 --> 00:17:00,550
Hanya bisa makan roti kukus...

231
00:17:00,860 --> 00:17:04,000
...dan minum semangkuk susu kedelai
yang rasanya aneh.

232
00:17:04,320 --> 00:17:06,720
Kalau begitu, kubawakan bahan baku
dari Shanghai ke sana.

233
00:17:06,720 --> 00:17:08,120
Kubuatkan langsung untukmu.

234
00:17:08,120 --> 00:17:10,170
♪Bagaimanakah cara menuliskan
akhir yang indah?♪

235
00:17:10,170 --> 00:17:16,100
♪Aku takut terikat denganmu
